import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Tabs, Space } from 'antd';
const { TabPane } = Tabs;

const Tab = () => (
  <Space size={100} >
    <Tabs defaultActiveKey="1" centered>
        <TabPane tab="With Emails" key="1">
          <Link to='/withEmails'>
            With Emails
          </Link>
        </TabPane>
        <TabPane tab="Without Emails" key="2">
          <Link to='/withoutEmails'>
            Without Emails
          </Link>
        </TabPane>
    </Tabs>
  </Space>

);

export default Tab
